The MIT license above covers Scriptoscope's own first-party source code (e.g. `src/`,
`tools/` first-party files, `scripts/`, `demo/` code). It does NOT relicense the
third-party material bundled in this repository, which keeps its own terms:

- `themes/<slug>/` — assets extracted from community-authored Kaleidoscope schemes.
  Each carries its original author's terms and provenance in `themes/<slug>/meta.json`
  (`origin.originalLicense`, `sourceUrl`) and `themes/<slug>/PROVENANCE.md`. These are
  redistributed under the original authors' freeware-with-redistribution terms, NOT MIT.
- `tools/sit-wasm/munbox/` — a vendored subset of munbox (https://github.com/idolpx/munbox),
  MIT-licensed; see `tools/sit-wasm/munbox/LICENSE`.
- `demo/assets/fonts/` — Charcoal 12 (Jeremy Sachs, CC BY-SA) and Virtue (Marty Pfeiffer,
  free-with-credit); see the license files alongside them.

See the "License" section of `README.md` for the full breakdown.
